<%- include('partials/header')%>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="content-header">
            <h1 style="text-align: center;">
                <strong>
                    Hi!
                </strong>
                Welcome to my website.
            </h1>
            <img src="/img/pfp.png" alt='profile picture' width="64" class="profile-pic">
            <style>
                @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
                    .profile-pic {
                        display: none;
                    }
                }
            </style>
            <div style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;">
                <h2 style="margin-block: 0;">
                    <span class="discord-contact-label">
                        <i class="fab fa-discord" style="color: #5865F2;"></i>
                        skybird2333#3209
                    </span>
                    <span class="tag l-<%= presence %>">
                        <%= presence.toUpperCase() %>
                    </span>
                </h2>
                <b>
                    Web & Discord bot developer, Minecraft addon creator, Gamer
                </b>
            </div>
            <div class="info">
                <p>
                    I have remastered my portfolio.
                    <a href="/portfolio" class="link">Check it out!</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-content">
            <h1>Nonsense stuff I write</h1>
            <% for(const post of postList) {%>
                <% if(!post) continue %>
                <div class="card outline">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <a href="/posts/<%=post.id %>" class="link">
                            <%=post.title %>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div style="color: var(--foreground-secondary)">
                        <%=post.subtitle %>
                    </div>

                    <% if(post.tags) {%>
                        <div style="margin-top: 7px">
                            <% for(const tag of post.tags) {%>
                                <a class="tag link" href="/tags/<%=tag %>">
                                    <%=tag %>
                                </a>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                <% if(!postList.length) {%>
                    None yet. Try refreshing?
                <% } %>
                    
                    <h1>My projects</h1>
                    <div style="color: var(--foreground-secondary);">
                        Click on one to learn more!
                    </div>

                    <br>


                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            Math tools vue

                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            A simple web app for linear and trig calculations in Mathematics.<br>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button button-github" href="https://github.com/skybird23333/math-tools-vue">
                                    Github Repository
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <div style="float: right">
                                <img src="/img/js-icon.png" width=32 alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            Ghost pinger

                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            A configurable script to spam ghost ping someone in a Discord server.<br>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button button-github" href="https://github.com/skybird23333/ghost-pinger">
                                    Github Repository
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <div style="float: right">
                                <img src="/img/js-icon.png" width=32 alt="">
                                <img src="/img/djs-icon.png" width=32 alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            UHC Function Addon
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            A lightweight, compatible, fully customizable addon for hosting UHC Games, large or
                            small.<br>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button button-github"
                                    href="https://github.com/skybird23333/mc-bedrocc-UHC-function">
                                    Github Repository
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button button-mcpedl" href="https://mcpedl.com/uhc-function-addon">
                                    MCPEDL Page
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            Corecoder: Develop
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hanprogramer/corecoder_develop/main/.github/Screenshot_CC3.png"
                                alt="" style="width: 100%">

                            Extensible cross-platform IDE for Android and Desktop. Featuring Syntax highlighting, fast
                            startup, and extensible plugins.<br>

                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button-github button"
                                    href="https://github.com/Hanprogramer/corecoder_develop">
                                    Project Repository
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>

                            <div style="float: right">
                                <img src="/img/flutter-icon.jpg" width=32 alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            Meds Addon
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            Meds addon brings modern medicines such as bandages and pills into Minecraft, providing a
                            lightweight and convenient alternative to healing other than vanilla potions.<br>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button-mcpedl button" href="https://mcpedl.com/meds-addon/">
                                    MCPEDL Page
                                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-collapsible">
                        <div class="card-collapsible-header">
                            Airdrop Addon
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            The airdrop addon adds airdrops into Minecraft survival mode, and also a flare gun that can
                            be
                            crafted.
                            <br>
                            <span class="button-container">
                                <a class="button-mcpedl button" href="https://mcpedl.com/airdrop-addon/">
                                    MCPEDL Page
                                </a>
                            </span>
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                   </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>

        .discord-contact-label {
            padding: 3px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .l-online {
            background-color: #04AA6D;
        }
        
        .l-dnd {
            background-color: #ff0000;
        }

        .l-idle {
            background-color: #e6b839;
        }

        .l-offline {
            background-color: #3a3a3a;
        }
    </style>
    <%- include('partials/footer')%>